^B@2^*BHoward: ^*N|cp||at|Many people bypass diamonds if they have a 4-card major. The main reason for that is, with many people like me preempting all the time, it is often better to get your major suits in as early as possible. However, 1D is an OK bid, as long as you don't play that you bypass diamonds in favor of a major.|
